repo_description: React and GraphQL implementation of the Maprunner WOC DB

schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
type Country {
  abbr: String
  country: String
  code: String
}

type WOC {
  id: Int
  type: String
  year: Int
  country: Country
  location: String
  dates: String
  countries: Int
  runners: Int
}

type Name {
  id: Int
  name: String
  plainname: String
  personid: Int
  nameid: Int
}

enum Type {
  WOC
  JWOC
}

enum Class {
  Men
  Women
}

enum Race {
  Long
  LongQualA
  LongQualB
  LongQualC
  LongQual1
  LongQual2
  LongQual3
  Short
  ShortQualA
  ShortQualB
  ShortQualC
  ShortQualD
  Middle
  MiddleQualA
  MiddleQualB
  MiddleQualC
  MiddleQual1
  MiddleQual2
  MiddleQual4
  Sprint
  SprintQualA
  SprintQualB
  SprintQualC
  SprintQual1
  SprintQual2
  SprintQual3
  Relay
  SprintRelay
}

type Result {
  id: Int
  position: Int
  name: String
  country: Country
  time: String
  seconds: Int
  secsdown: String
  percentdown: Float
  class: Class
  race: Race
  year: Int
  raceid: Int
  woc: WOC
  final: Int
  nameid: Int
  personid: Int
  points: Int
}

type Query {
  allWOCs: [WOC]
  bestResult(type: Type!, class: Class!, race: Race!, country: String): [Result]
}
